sequenceDiagram
    participant B as Buyer Agent
    participant R as AVP Registry
    participant T as Trust Authority
    participant V as Vendor Agent

    Note over B: User searches for "Java + Travel dev companies"

    B->>R: Search(technologies=java, domains=travel)
    R-->>B: List of matching vendors

    loop For each vendor
        B->>V: GET /.well-known/avp.json
        V-->>B: Discovery Document

        B->>T: Verify vendor trust score
        T-->>B: Trust score + verification level
    end

    Note over B: Filter by trust score threshold

    B->>V: POST /avp/handshake (signed)
    V->>T: Verify buyer identity
    T-->>V: Buyer verified
    V-->>B: Session token + policies

    B->>V: POST /avp/rfp (with requirements)
    Note over V: AI generates proposal
    V-->>B: Proposal (pricing, timeline, team)

    Note over B: AI analyzes and ranks proposals

    opt Negotiation
        B->>V: POST /avp/negotiate (counter-proposal)
        V-->>B: Adjusted proposal
        B->>V: POST /avp/negotiate/accept
        V-->>B: Acceptance confirmed
    end

    B->>V: POST /avp/settle (final terms)
    V-->>B: Settlement confirmation
    V->>R: Record transaction
